      "writtenOn": "2021-01-15T13:59:39Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Ben, thank you very much for taking the time to do an initial review, i\u0027s great to have your feedback! Yes, I believe we can move the API to a behaviour where it does apply the FT_Face size and transform, so that we don\u0027t have to go through extra steps to work in font unit space again.",
