      },
      "writtenOn": "2021-01-15T13:59:39Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Ok, if I understand your earlier comment regarding FT_Face\u0027s size and possible FT_Transform, then your request is to concatenate those before returning anything from the API, which would then still be y-up, and then turn it into y-down here by negating the fields that you mentioned. Formatting aside, is that what you have in mind here?",
      "parentUuid": "12cfd2db_29b8c0d7",
      "revId": "85b37637cbc8e77babcc641bad511013f1b608ea",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02"
    },
