      "writtenOn": "2021-01-15T15:13:57Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Yeah, I think that\u0027s right.\n\nI was just looking at my comments and maybe I should start marking them Comment#1, Comment#2, etc at the top to give a better reading order. The order in which the comments show up in the file isn\u0027t really the order I wrote them in and it\u0027s difficult to make them actually independent without a lot of repetition. Also, I always end up writing the overall review comment last, so it\u0027s kinda an abstract, but it looks like it came first even though it was written last. Order and structure in communication is interesting.",
