      "writtenOn": "2021-01-20T16:16:36Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Now relying on work-in-progress https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/drott/freetype/-/tree/internalScaling - (so far only applies x_scale and y_scale, still issues with PaintRotate and radial gradients when a transform is applied to FT_Face.",
      "parentUuid": "52d21900_5771bd50",
      "revId": "85b37637cbc8e77babcc641bad511013f1b608ea",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02"
